graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:CommonCreateAttachmentInput!)
{
	commonCreateAttachment (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		familyId
		attachableId
		sort
		alt
		title
		originFilename
		filename
		mimetype
		extension
		relativePathSegments
		width
		height
		size
		url
		isCropable
		libraryId
		libraryFilename
		meta
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	commonGetAttachments (query: $query)
	{
		id
		attachableId
		sort
		alt
		title
		originFilename
		filename
		mimetype
		extension
		relativePathSegments
		width
		height
		size
		url
		isCropable
		libraryFilename
		meta
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
